news.title: Dubai's high-end property sales rise on overseas demand
news.para: A total of 105 homes worth an overall $1.73 billion were sold from January to March, up from around $1.6 billion a year earlier, according to property consultancy Knight Frank.

news.title: Hayrana RERA Court imposes fine on Vatika for violating builder-buyer agreement
news.para: The landmark order of the RERA court passed by Judge SK Arora has come as a big relief for the five complainants, the official said.

news.title: PWC rejects allegations over China Evergrande Group’s audit
news.para: Accounting firm PwC on Monday rejected an anonymous letter that criticised the company's involvement in auditing beleaguered Chinese real estate giant Evergrande, saying the letter contained "false allegations".

news.title: Homebuilder confidence in USA holds steady in April
news.para: Measures of current sales and prospective buyer traffic both ticked up to their highest levels since August while the survey's measure of sales in the next six months slipped.

news.title: New home prices in China drop by 2.2% in March
news.para: New home prices in March dropped 2.2% from a year earlier, marking the biggest decline since August 2015, and worse than a 1.4% fall in February, according to Reuters calculations based on National Bureau of Statistics (NBS) data.

news.title: Punjab and Haryana HC stays all constructions in green belts of Sirsa
news.para: The main allegations are that local political leaders, including Gopal Kanda and his brother Gobind Kanda, have been supporting the encroachments through their political clout.

news.title: Hyderabad civic body offers paid pickup service for C&D waste
news.para: Citizens can visit GHMC website online services construction & demolition waste pick up service request, My GHMC app or toll-free number.

news.title: South Goa district magistrate asks owners to verify tenants properly
news.para: The magistrate has directed that the verification must be carried out through proof of identity such as election card, driving licence, Aadhaar card, passport, etc.

news.title: Lucknow civic body offers 15% discount on property tax till June 30
news.para: Municipal commissioner Inderjit Singh said, “We previously offered a 10% discount for timely tax payment. We’ve decided to increase this by an additional 5%.”

news.title: Sebi to auction 30 properties of seven companies in May 2024
news.para: Markets regulator Sebi on Monday said it will auction 30 properties of seven companies, including Mangalam Agro Products and Purusattam Infotech Industries, on May 15 to recover money illegally collected from investors.

news.title: Funds for rural housing scheme okayed till September 2024
news.para: The finance ministry has approved the release of funds for six more months through September 2024 under the Indian government's flagship housing scheme, Pradhan Mantri Awaas Yojana-Gramin (PMAY-G).

news.title: CG Group has plans to list hotel business in next few years
news.para: CG Group's CG Hospitality Global and The Fern brand aim for gradual public launch. Expansion strategies include EBITDA growth, strategic investor involvement, IPO launch, The Farm introduction, Taj properties, a Dubai hotel, safari lodge expansion.

news.title: Residents may move Delhi HC with evacuation plea for Signature View Apartments
news.para: The apartment has 10 towers with a stilt+10 storied structure and two towers with a stilt+6 storied structure. While the matter is listed for hearing in the high court on April 22, last month.

news.title: SC to examine validity of Rs 33,000 crore income tax claim on Jaypee Infratech
news.para: The Supreme Court will review the validity of the Income-Tax commissioner's assessment of Jaypee Infratech Ltd (JIL), which raised a claim of ₹33,000 crore.

news.title: Wellknown Polyester's CMD buys two flats in Mumbai's Malabar Hill for Rs 270 crore
news.para: The transaction values the apartment at Rs 1.41 lakh per sq ft. The buyers have paid over Rs 16.20 crore as stamp duty alone for the registration of the deals that took place on Friday, showed the documents accessed through IndexTap.com.

news.title: Standard Chartered has no intention to divest Chennai property
news.para: Baashyaaam Constructions is present in luxury residential projects, apart from commercial and hospitality. It is developing an uber-luxury twin-tower project at the site of the erstwhile five-star Crowne Plaza hotel in Chennai’s Adyar Park.

news.title: Kolkata civic body takes tough stand against unauthorised buildings
news.para: Each stop-work order should be brought to the notice of the executive engineers in the boroughs concerned, who will contact local cops and seek assistance in case of demolition.

news.title: New home prices in Germany rise by 2.5% in FY24
news.para: Prices for existing apartments fell 2.5% in the first quarter of 2024 from a year earlier, according to the figures by ImmoScout24, an online property platform.

news.title: China Vanke says it faces short-term liquidity pressure
news.para: Investors have been selling off Vanke's shares and bonds in the past few weeks on liquidity concerns, triggering a rare central government directive to help the Shenzhen-based company.

news.title: NCLT disposes case of bankruptcy plea filed by SBI, IDBI against Mumbai Metro One
news.para: An application under Section 7 of Insolvency and Bankruptcy Code (IBC) is initiated by a financial creditor either on their own or jointly with other financial creditors for initiation of Corporate Insolvency Resolution Process against a corporate debtor.
